snippet.title: Earth of Oryn city builder - The 4 biomes with gameplay
snippet.description:
Earth of Oryn is an indie city-builder/strategy game in a medieval world filled with story and heart.

Here is a small preview of the game as it looks in early July 2024.

You can wishlist the game on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1972450/Earth_of_Oryn/

You can also follow the development of the game on other social networks:
Discord http://discord.gg/WD2RTE6uE2
Website https://earthoforyn.com
Twitter https://twitter.com/EarthOfOryn
